name: Seek Navigation system
description: Not everyone in the world can own a car. If you own a car, there are still many issues you might face in big cities like New York and London. Due to endless problems with traffic, parking, and car maintenance, most people prefer to hire a taxi then owning a car. Based on these facts, we can say that on-demand-ride-hailing services like Uber will find their users all over the world, which leads us to a simple fact that this is an attractive niche for many entrepreneurs.
